<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>消费者权益 on 曹义德律师专栏</title><link>https://caoyide.com/tags/%E6%B6%88%E8%B4%B9%E8%80%85%E6%9D%83%E7%9B%8A/</link><description>Recent content in 消费者权益 on 曹义德律师专栏</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 01:20:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://caoyide.com/tags/%E6%B6%88%E8%B4%B9%E8%80%85%E6%9D%83%E7%9B%8A/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>快递丢了，快递公司说只赔三倍运费——合法吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%92%E4%B8%A2%E5%A4%B1/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 01:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-10-%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%92%E4%B8%A2%E5%A4%B1/</guid><description>寄了一个包裹值两千块，快递丢了。快递公司说你没保价，只赔三倍运费也就是三十块。合理吗？</description></item><item><title>网购的东西不想要了，商家说拆了包装不给退——合法吗？</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E4%B8%83%E5%A4%A9%E6%97%A0%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E9%80%80%E8%B4%A7/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-09-%E4%B8%83%E5%A4%A9%E6%97%A0%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1%E9%80%80%E8%B4%A7/</guid><description>网购的东西拆了包装还能退吗？哪些商品不适用七天无理由？商家拒退怎么办？</description></item><item><title>买了保险出了事，保险公司说这不赔那不赔——怎么让他赔</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E4%BF%9D%E9%99%A9%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%8B%92%E8%B5%94/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:40:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E4%BF%9D%E9%99%A9%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%8B%92%E8%B5%94/</guid><description>买了保险，出了事找保险公司理赔，对方翻出合同里的一条免责条款说这事不在理赔范围——怎么办？</description></item><item><title>装修装了三分之一，老板跑了——剩下的钱和烂摊子怎么办</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E8%A3%85%E4%BF%AE%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%B7%91%E8%B7%AF/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 00:20:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-08-%E8%A3%85%E4%BF%AE%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%B7%91%E8%B7%AF/</guid><description>装修公司收了钱跑路了，家里水电没做完、地砖铺了一半、墙上到处是坑。已经付的十几万装修款怎么追？</description></item><item><title>买到了假货，除了退货还能让他赔你三倍</title><link>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%81%87%E8%B4%A7%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8D%E8%B5%94%E5%81%BF/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 02:50:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://caoyide.com/posts/2026-05-07-%E5%81%87%E8%B4%A7%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8D%E8%B5%94%E5%81%BF/</guid><description>买到假货别光退货。法律规定经营者欺诈的退一赔三，最低赔五百。很多人不知道这条，白白吃亏。</description></item></channel></rss>